title: Magistrate Orders Fox Guest Wayne Simmons to Jail for Falsely Claiming CIA Ties
text:
Published By: Media Ite - Today 
Wayne Simmons was ordered to jail by a federal judge today as he continues to face criminal charges for falsely claim to be an ex-CIA agent....
